snippet: At Grass valley, Aug. 3, of erysipelas, William Mounger formerly from Washington Co., Ala., aged about 30 years. In Nevada, John Hernundez, a native of the Chili Islands aged 23 years....
lead_paragraph: At Grass valley, Aug. 3, of erysipelas, William Mounger formerly from Washington Co., Ala., aged about 30 years. In Nevada, John Hernundez, a native of the Chili Islands aged 23 years.
